songs.title: Taur
songs.lyrics:
(Intro)
Ho fir da Bugatti yaar 150 te chaddi

(Verse 1)(Bohemia)
Vairi bada lagande zor
Par gali gali mera shor
Main foreign ch rehna
Meri 25 pindan ch Taur
Maine badli ni Topi
Badle ni Nike
Par jis din da aaya
Maine badal ditti gayaki
Vairi bada lagande zor
Par ajj vi mera daur
Main ajj ae vi betha 5 star ch naal Gippy Grewal
Meri lifestyle jive movie
Main movie star bina movie
Mere rap ch gap ni mera best attack
Tu sale rap kare mere wangu tu vi

(Bridge)
Gallan karda nai vaddi na
Ainve marda ni addi
Na Ajj fukreya di chalni ni
Ajj mitraan ne taur kaddi

(Chorus)(Gippy Grewal)
Ajj mitran ne taur kaddi
Ajj mitran ne taur kaddi
Ajj mitran ne taur kaddi
Ho firda bugatti yaar 150 te chhadi..(2x)

(Verse 2)(Gippy Grewal)
Black gaddi black kurta pajama
Main pairan ch Dunatii shauq naal pavan
Chandigarh Mohali mera sirnava
Main leke sports car hath na aawa
Main kisse de culture nu kehnda nayio fake
Gurdas Maan di rees kithon kar lu Drake
Main karda ni aape dikh di ae gal vaat vaddi

(Chorus)(Gippy Grewal)
Aaj mitraan ne taur kadi
Aaj mitraan ne taur kadi
Aaj mitraan ne taur kadi
Ho firda Bugatti yaar 150 te chaddi..(2x)

(Verse 3) (Bohemia)
Liquor store ton chakki botal main waddi
Hun ek sau di speed te chale meri gaddi
Dono jebaan ch meri notan di thaddi aaja..
Ajj mitran ne taur kaddi
Tenu chakkan lai le aaya
Main two door gaddi
Naale kudiyan nu main karda na
Bore kadi billo
Aapan kaddi di ae taur kadi kadi billo
Ajj mitran ne taur kaddi

(Verse 4) (Bohemia)
Sadda mitraan de siran te
Sache yaar unglan te gina de
Gaddi meri chaley akhan band agge vekhan ki
Saare mere pichhay kakh meri raah te
Munde behnde meri jaga te
Gallan karn vaddi vaddi
Uss din mitran di sui ad gayi
Jis din mitran ne taur kaddi

(Verse 5)(Gippy Grewal)
Dollar aan nal mitraan ne dicky full kari aa
Tan hi har sohni kudi daini light hari aa..(2x)

(Chorus) (Gippy Grewal)
Ho firda bugatti yaar 150 te chhaddi
Aaj mitraan ne taur kaddi
Aaj mitraan ne taur kaddi
Ajj mitraan ne taur kaddi
Ho jehde bann de star saale phir de ne palle addi

(Outro+Chorus) (Gippy Grewal)
Aaj mitran ne taur kaddi
Aaj mitran ne taur kaddi
Aaj mitran ne taur kaddi
Ho firda Bugatti yaar 150 te chaddi..(3x)
